[It's always nice to have a "no new cases" post with respect to the situation of MERS-CoV in Saudi Arabia. The current tally of laboratory confirmed cases of MERS-CoV infection reported by Saudi Arabia since June 2012 remains at 1038 cases, including 459 deaths, with a reported case fatality rate of 44.2 percent. A map showing the location of Riyadh in Saudi Arabia can be found at the source URL. - Mod.MPP]

